OOC: All right I know this is technically moding but I hope you won't mind 
Airly. :) of course if you do it's only an attempted shove.

::Aerotaur::
       He's still lost in the quarters area of the ship wandering around in 
search of fruit.  In his wanderings he returns to the hallway where Empath's 
quarters are when he comes across Windlord in Empath's door.  "Why hello 
there my fine feathered friend and how are you today?"  He continues walking 
past Windlord giving him a gentle shove into her room and closes the door 
behind him.  He continues to walk in search of fruit totally oblivious to his 
surroundings.

--part1_fb.32e9b923.2b32a085_boundary
